BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Chapter 1: Understanding Thyroid Health) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 674.2 Td (What Does the Thyroid Do?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 656.2 Td (The thyroid is a butterfly-shaped gland in your neck that produces hormones controlling) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 642.2 Td (metabolism, energy, temperature, heart rate, brain function, and virtually every cell in) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 628.2 Td (your body.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 600.4 Td (Key Thyroid Hormones) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 584.4 Td (- TSH \(Thyroid Stimulating Hormone\): Brain's message to thyroid) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 570.4 Td (- T4 \(Thyroxine\): Inactive storage form \(produced by thyroid\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 556.4 Td (- T3 \(Triiodothyronine\): Active form \(converted from T4 in body\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 542.4 Td (- Reverse T3: Inactive T3 \(produced during stress\)) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 512.6 Td (Hypothyroidism \(Underactive\)) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 490.6 Td (Common Symptoms) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 474.6 Td (- Fatigue and sluggishness) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 460.6 Td (- Weight gain or inability to lose weight) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 446.6 Td (- Cold intolerance) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 432.6 Td (- Constipation) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 418.6 Td (- Dry skin and brittle nails) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 404.6 Td (- Hair loss \(including outer third of eyebrows\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 390.6 Td (- Brain fog and poor memory) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 376.6 Td (- Depression and low mood) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 362.6 Td (- Muscle aches and joint pain) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 348.6 Td (- Heavy or irregular periods) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 334.6 Td (- High cholesterol) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 304.8 Td (Hashimoto's Thyroiditis) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 286.8 Td (Hashimoto's is an autoimmune condition where the immune system attacks the thyroid gland.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 272.8 Td (It is the most common cause of hypothyroidism.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 258.8 Td (- Affects 5% of the population \(10x more common in women\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 244.8 Td (- Diagnosed by thyroid antibodies \(TPO, TgAb\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 230.8 Td (- Can fluctuate between hypo and hyper symptoms) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 216.8 Td (- Autoimmune = immune system dysfunction, not just thyroid) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 202.8 Td (- Often occurs alongside other autoimmune conditions) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
