BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Chapter 6: Lifestyle & Supplements) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 674.2 Td (Medication Tips) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 656.2 Td (- Take thyroid medication first thing, on empty stomach) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 642.2 Td (- Wait 30-60 minutes before eating) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 628.2 Td (- Wait 4 hours before calcium, iron, or coffee) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 614.2 Td (- Take at the same time daily) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 600.2 Td (- Do not stop or change dose without doctor guidance) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 570.4 Td (Supplements for Thyroid/Hashimoto's) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 552.4 Td (- Selenium: 200mcg daily \(critical for Hashimoto's - reduces antibodies\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 538.4 Td (- Vitamin D3: 2000-5000 IU \(test and optimize\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 524.4 Td (- Zinc: 15-30mg daily) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 510.4 Td (- B-complex: Energy and conversion support) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 496.4 Td (- Magnesium glycinate: 200-400mg) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 482.4 Td (- Iron: Only if deficient \(test ferritin\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 468.4 Td (- Omega-3: Anti-inflammatory) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 438.6 Td (Stress Management \(Critical for Hashimoto's\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 420.6 Td (Stress directly suppresses thyroid function and increases autoimmune activity.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 406.6 Td (- Adaptogenic herbs: Ashwagandha \(caution: may not suit all thyroid conditions\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 392.6 Td (- Daily meditation or breathwork) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 378.6 Td (- Adequate sleep \(8+ hours for thyroid patients\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 364.6 Td (- Gentle exercise \(avoid overexercise with hypothyroidism\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 350.6 Td (- Set boundaries and reduce obligations) Tj ET
endstream
